:

1. *Pravimo* našu budućnost. (We are creating our future.)
2. Oni *prave* planove za leto. (They are making plans for summer.)
3. Moj prijatelj *pravi* lutke od papira. (My friend is making paper dolls.)
4. Ona *pravi* sladoled za svoju decu. (She is making ice cream for her children.)
5. Oni *prave* zajedničku budućnost. (They are making a shared future.)
6. Mi *pravimo* dobre odluke. (We are making good decisions.)